<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Radiant Systems.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Radiant Systems.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-27</dateline>
<text>
<p>Deutsche Morgan Grenfell said it reiterated a buy rating on Radiant Systems Inc.</p>
<p>-- said expects Radiant Systems to win a $500 million contract from PepsiCo Inc.</p>
<p>-- Additional details were not immediately available.</p>
<p>-- Radiant Systems lost 1/2 to 14-7/8.</p>
